* Leading architectural and engineering reviews of proposed IT investments/solutions to determine the strategic alignment and technical soundness; Working on abstract concepts and leading projects with strategic significance involving complex variables;
* Offering seasoned advice on application solutions including assisting with planning and architectural design, development, resolution of technical issues, and application rationalization;
* Overseeing and establishing delivery of project initiatives;
* Building trusting and influential relationships at all levels and engaging with vendors and third parties as appropriate;
* Assessing the viability and feasibility of 3rd party solutions to meet business goals. Advise and influence project sponsors and teams on the technical directions;
* Collaborating with other Solution Architects and Developers to provide technical design guidance that will align with the strategy and applicable technical standards;
* Working independently to evaluate and make strategic decisions that will address specific technology design needs and issues within their technology area;
* Owning and driving thought leadership to influence their sphere of technology in the use of innovation to advance business capabilities; Advising and influencing leaders on trends that could potentially affect the success of a function or business area;
* Understanding emerging technologies to market these technologies to business leadership and convey possibilities for new ways of working;
* Assembling concepts and communications appropriate for specific audiences at all staff levels;
* Promoting a culture of innovation by continuously seeking opportunities for improvement within role, processes, team and the IT organisation as a whole;
